---
title: Slammin’ Secret Sauce Chicken Sandwiches with Scallion Cabbage Slaw
description: Tonight's installment of “name that chicken sandwich’ is a slam dunk. BBQ-seasoned chicken is topped with our secret sauce, and served with a scallion cabbage slaw on the side. Ready to guess those secret ingredients? Spoiler alert: it involves pickles. That’s all we’ll share for now, you’ll have to wait until this one lands at your door. Trust us, you’ll want to make this sauce over and over again.
